        "created_at": "2019-06-05T08:35:24.541Z",
        "cooked": "<p>A related question: What about the number of the proxies? The FDB architecture document only states the minimum number for class=stateless processes is 4 proxies. Should that  the number of the proxies be increased with the number of the storage pods as well, or the number can be fixed?</p>",
